>>__ Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="hol"};
## `DISJ1`

``` hol4
Thm.DISJ1 : thm -> term -> thm
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Introduces a right disjunct into the conclusion of a theorem.

``` hol4
       A |- t1
   ---------------  DISJ1 (A |- t1) t2
    A |- t1 \/ t2
```

### Failure

Fails unless the term argument is boolean.

### Example

``` hol4
>> DISJ1 TRUTH F;
```

